{
  "name": "Attributes & Prime Modifier",
  "pages": [
    {
      "_id": "b83dabc39c7323ca",
      "name": "Attributes",
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
      "sort": 1,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8115-8528-e2c3be591f0e\">There are <strong>4</strong> Attributes in DC20 that represent your Physical (Might &amp; Agility) and Mental (Intelligence &amp; Charisma) abilities. Each Attribute has a\n\t\t\t\tvalue that ranges from <strong>-2</strong> to <strong>+7 </strong>(for most creatures) which measures your\n\t\t\t\taptitude with that Attribute.</p><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-818d-9219-d8093286fc29\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Might = your Strength of Body.</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8142-90c0-db5753d7b873\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Agility = your Balance, Nimbleness, and\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDexterity.</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8107-8217-d9a7de03edfd\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Intelligence = your Reasoning, Understanding,\n\t\t\t\t\t\tand Wisdom.</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-81b9-ae72-e17a7163e8c9\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Charisma = your Charm, Presence,\n\t\t\t\t\t\tPersuasiveness, and Force of Will.</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8153-9c85-ec79e0774350\" class=\"block-color-blue_background\"><strong>Example:</strong> If you\n\t\t\t\thave an Agility of <strong>3</strong>, then you would add <strong>+3</strong> to any d20 roll that uses Agility.\n\t\t\t</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 1,
        "show": true
      },
      "type": "text",
