    },
    {
      "_id": "ac7a5b7ab8c0c51f",
      "name": "Standard Array",
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
      "sort": 7,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8141-8a4c-debcaf609002\">You start with an array of <strong>3</strong>,\n\t\t\t\t<strong>1</strong>, <strong>0</strong>, <strong>-2</strong> and assign each value to an Attribute of your\n\t\t\t\tchoice. You then gain <strong>2</strong> additional Attribute Points to increase whichever Attributes you want,\n\t\t\t\tup to the Attribute Limit (3).</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 3,
        "show": true
      },
      "type": "text",
      "system": {},
      "image": {},
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
      "flags": {},
      "_stats": {
        "compendiumSource": null,
        "duplicateSource": null,
        "coreVersion": "13.344",
        "systemId": "dc20rpg",
        "systemVersion": "0.9.0",
        "createdTime": null,
        "modifiedTime": null,
        "lastModifiedBy": null,
        "exportSource": null
      },
      "category": null,
      "_key": "!journal.pages!lPNREZ3AfO40mAeV.ac7a5b7ab8c0c51f"
    },
    {
      "_id": "94e13196946757c1",
      "name": "Point Buy",
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
      "sort": 8,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8153-ab1c-cd367927da16\">You start with a <strong>-2</strong> in all of your\n\t\t\t\tAttributes. You then gain <strong>12 </strong>Attribute Points to increase whichever Attributes you want, up to\n\t\t\t\tthe Attribute Limit (3).</p><p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-81b2-ba3a-c76c20544930\" class=\"block-color-purple_background\"><strong>DC Tip:</strong> Your\n\t\t\t\tPrime Modifier (see later in this chapter) comes from your highest Attribute, so it’s a good idea to make sure\n\t\t\t\tthat you get a 3 in at least one of your Attributes. </p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 3,
        "show": true
      },
      "type": "text",
      "system": {},
      "image": {},
      "video": {
