    {
      "_id": "3f1a9cf130da6e49",
      "name": "Prime Modifier",
      "ownership": {
        "default": -1
      },
      "sort": 12,
      "text": {
        "content": "<p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-81c9-96ad-d149fb92c9c5\" class=\"block-color-pink\">Your Prime\n\t\t\t\t\tModifier represents your overall experience and prowess as an adventurer. You use your Prime Modifier as the\n\t\t\t\t\tprimary bonus you add to Checks involving attacking, casting a Spell, or overall awareness of dangers around\n\t\t\t\t\tyou. Your Prime Modifier is commonly associated with the following:</p><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-819e-80e7-c2d4cd2d8e24\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Attack Checks (made to Attack with a Weapon or\n\t\t\t\t\t\tUnarmed Strike).</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-818b-bbbe-ce1d4d78fd16\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Spell Checks (made to cast a Spell or use a\n\t\t\t\t\t\tsupernatural ability).</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-811c-a039-dea3a3a40164\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Save DCs (the difficulty of resisting the\n\t\t\t\t\t\teffects you impose on other creatures).</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><ul id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8156-8499-ef8b0363ede3\" class=\"bulleted-list\">\n\t\t\t\t<li style=\"list-style-type:disc\">Awareness Checks (your ability to perceive and\n\t\t\t\t\t\tdetect things around you).</li>\n\t\t\t</ul><p id=\"1cf1b90a-e081-8124-aec5-e392ba30c901\" class=\"block-color-purple_background\"><strong>DC Tip:</strong> The\n\t\t\t\tBarbarian in the group having a high Charisma instead of Might doesn’t make him worse at swinging a sword.</p>",
        "format": 1
      },
      "title": {
        "level": 1,
        "show": true
      },
      "type": "text",
